797.1628, 798.8025, 797.8678, 797.8212, 797.7139, 797.0923, 797.2337, 797.3766, 798.2427, 797.4517, 797.2632, 796.3046, 796.3027, 795.954, 797.2854, 796.7991, 797.0466, 797.1813, 797.3755, 797.8231, 796.4197, 796.2008, 795.538, 796.1424, 795.0429, 794.6313, 792.9088, 793.5957, 793.1997, 793.3266, 793.6028, 794.6211, 794.8288, 794.6417, 795.016, 795.9008, 795.1546, 795.8989, 794.7378, 794.3799, 794.4649, 793.8939, 794.2101, 794.8322, 795.9462, 796.7584, 794.6509, 795.3945, 794.6795, 795.6247, 796.1855, 795.9136, 794.5518, 793.9817, 794.4468, 793.6925, 794.328, 794.469, 795.2084, 794.8955, 795.0643, 795.0008, 795.0825, 793.9337, 793.4573, 793.1128, 792.6069, 792.1208, 792.3149, 793.2428, 793.3588, 795.4764, 796.0079, 795.3274, 795.1324, 796.1028, 797.3302, 796.7874, 797.3565, 797.2471, 796.7924, 799.6257, 802.6067, 801.2719, 802.3149, 801.439, 801.867, 801.749, 801.1351, 800.5267, 798.5578, 798.3874, 799.9429, 799.2209, 797.7137, 796.044, 795.7612, 793.9639, 796.0317, 798.4641, 798.8656, 799.3032, 798.3646, 797.2273, 797.3914, 796.4998, 794.5555, 794.9961, 793.6455, 792.617, 791.8761, 791.2235, 790.013, 787.2575, 789.8438, 787.361, 788.8949, 790.7304, 788.7004, 787.5021, 788.3295, 785.2297, 788.7205, 785.9236, 784.8334, 780.4918, 776.5673, 779.7902, 782.5808, 779.944, 784.6015, 779.9315, 777.1663, 779.1554, 778.3901, 783.3871], "summary_html": "<h1>COVID-19 and Commodity Pricing Premium</h1>\n<p><strong>Sharpe 4.41 | 通过</strong></p>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本论文研究中国商品期货市场三个基准定价因子：基差（Basis）、动量（Momentum）和基差动量（Basis-Momentum）。核心发现是这三个因子的截面排名组合能够有效预测商品期货未来收益。基差因子捕捉套保者为转移价格风险而支付的期限结构溢价（backwardation品种预期收益更高）；动量因子捕捉过去一年的累积收益趋势；基差动量因子捕捉展期收益的动量，反映投机者流动性供给能力的变化。</p>\n<p>复现时将论文中的近远月价差（BR）映射为展期收益率（ry），将基差动量近似为ry的滚动累积。三因子截面排名后等权组合，用 final_cs 归一化确保零净敞口和固定杠杆，20日定期换仓。组合后的信号在所有品种上均有正的时序IC（91%品种），表明信号质量稳健。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>基差因子（Basis Ratio）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">BR_{i,t} = \\frac{F_{T_2,i,t}}{F_{T_1,i,t}} - 1 \\approx -ry_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>动量因子（Momentum）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M_{i,t} = \\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-244}} - 1</div>\n<p><strong>基差动量（Basis-Momentum）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">BM_{i,t} = \\sum_{s=t-244}^{t} ry_{i,s}</div>\n<p><strong>仓位归一化（final_cs）</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{PctRank}(\\text{signal}_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{demean}_{i,t} = \\text{rank}_{i,t} - \\overline{\\text{rank}}_t</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{demean}_{i,t}}{\\sum_j |\\text{demean}_{j,t}|}</div>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>mom_window</td><td>244</td><td>60-244</td><td>动量窗口（论文：244交易日 ~ 1年）</td></tr><tr><td>bm_window</td><td>244</td><td>60-244</td><td>基差动量累积窗口</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td>20</td><td>5-20</td><td>换仓间隔（论文用周频，20日更优）</td></tr><tr><td>ry_min_periods</td><td>60</td><td>30-120</td><td>BM计算最少有效数据天数</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (扣费后)</td><td><strong>4.41</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>26.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.95%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-2.44%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手率</td><td>3.2%</td></tr><tr><td>总交易成本</td><td>2.9%</td></tr><tr><td>NAV终值</td><td>3.38</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>Top 5 变体对比</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th></tr><tr><td>combo_all3_h20_raw</td><td>4.41</td><td>26.3%</td><td>-2.4%</td></tr><tr><td>combo_all3_h10_raw</td><td>4.41</td><td>25.9%</td><td>-2.1%</td></tr><tr><td>combo_all3_h20_cs</td><td>4.38</td><td>901%</td><td>-28.5%</td></tr><tr><td>combo_all3_raw (h5)</td><td>4.37</td><td>25.8%</td><td>-1.9%</td></tr><tr><td>combo_all3_h10_cs</td><td>4.34</td><td>890%</td><td>-28.5%</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.07</td><td>0.98</td><td>0.75</td><td>0.76</td><td>0.99</td><td>0.81</td><td>0.89</td><td>0.75</td><td>0.40</td><td>0.09</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1</strong> (Sharpe 4.37): 初始实现三个因子（basis用ry，momentum用244日累计收益，basis-momentum用ry的244日滚动和），final_cs截面归一化，5日换仓。10个变体覆盖单因子（7个）+组合（3个）。组合因子combo_all3（三因子等权）表现最佳，截面IC=0.050，时序IC=0.042。</p>\n<p><strong>R2</strong> (Sharpe 4.37): 加入_cs和_ts归一化变体，共30个变体。_raw仍最优，_cs紧随其后（4.31），_ts表现下降。</p>\n<p><strong>R3</strong> (Sharpe 4.41, +0.9%): 关键突破来自延长换仓周期至20日：turnover从6.86%降至3.2%，Sharpe从4.37升至4.41。IC-gate过滤对已经91%正IC的信号效果有限。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（57个商品期货），黑色系(J/I/JM/RB)和化工(MA/P)贡献最大</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20日换仓，属于低频截面因子</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - basis单因子（用ry）表现为负Sharpe，需进一步验证方向\n<p>- 2024-2025年Sharpe下降（0.40/0.09），因子alpha可能衰减 - 论文使用近远月合约数据构建BR/BM，我们用ry/ry累积近似 - 组合因子的高Sharpe部分来自因子间低相关性的分散化效果</p>"}